---
// Bespoke homepage content
---

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section class="hero" role="banner">
  <div class="hero-bg" role="img" aria-label="大学校园留学生走路的场景"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span class="hero-badge-dot"></span>
      每月更新 · 覆盖 7 个热门留学目的地
    </div>
    <h1>一键算清<em>留学总花销</em><br>心里有底再出发</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">选国家 · 选学位 · 选城市，秒算学费 + 生活费 + 保险 + 机票全口径开销，费用构成一目了然</p>

    <!-- CALCULATOR CARD inside Hero -->
    <div class="calc-card" id="calculator" role="main">
      <div class="calc-tabs" role="tablist">
        <div class="calc-tab active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="calcPanel" tabindex="0" onclick="switchTab(this,'full')">📊 全口径费用测算</div>
        <div class="calc-tab" role="tab" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" onclick="switchTab(this,'compare')">🌏 国家横向对比</div>
        <div class="calc-tab" role="tab" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" onclick="switchTab(this,'budget')">💰 预算逆推</div>
      </div>
      <div class="calc-body" id="calcPanel">
        <!-- Full calc panel -->
        <div id="panelFull">
          <div class="calc-grid">
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label for="country">目的国 <span aria-hidden="true">🌍</span></label>
              <select id="country" onchange="onCountryChange()">
                <option value="">请选择国家</option>
                <option value="AU">🇦🇺 澳大利亚</option>
                <option value="UK">🇬🇧 英国</option>
                <option value="US">🇺🇸 美国</option>
                <option value="CA">🇨🇦 加拿大</option>
                <option value="NZ">🇳🇿 新西兰</option>
                <option value="SG">🇸🇬 新加坡</option>
                <option value="HK">🇭🇰 香港</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label for="degree">学位层次</label>
              <select id="degree">
                <option value="bachelor">本科 (3–4年)</option>
                <option value="master" selected>硕士 (1–2年)</option>
                <option value="phd">博士 (3–5年)</option>
                <option value="language">语言学校 (0.5–1年)</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label for="city">城市 / 地区</label>
              <select id="city">
                <option value="">请先选择国家</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label for="years">学习年限</label>
              <select id="years">
                <option value="0.5">0.5 年</option>
                <option value="1">1 年</option>
                <option value="1.5">1.5 年</option>
                <option value="2" selected>2 年</option>
                <option value="3">3 年</option>
                <option value="4">4 年</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button class="calc-btn" onclick="calculate()" aria-label="立即计算留学总费用">
            立即计算总费用
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M3 9h12M10 4l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </button>

          <!-- RESULT -->
          <div class="result-panel" id="resultPanel" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true">
            <div class="result-header">
              <div>
                <div class="result-total-label">留学总费用估算</div>
                <div class="result-total-amount" id="totalAmount">¥ 0</div>
                <div class="result-total-period" id="totalPeriod">计算中…</div>
              </div>
              <div class="result-disclaimer" role="note">
                <span>⚠️</span>
                <span>费用区间数据来源公开资料，<strong>仅供参考</strong>，实际以院校及当地生活为准</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="result-layout">
              <div class="donut-wrap" id="donutWrap">
                <svg id="donutSvg" width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 200 200" aria-label="费用构成环形图" role="img">
                  <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="75" fill="none" stroke="#F2F5F4" stroke-width="28"/>
                  <g id="donutArcs"></g>
                </svg>
                <div class="donut-center">
                  <div class="donut-center-pct" id="donutTopPct">—</div>
                  <div class="donut-center-lbl" id="donutTopLbl">学费占比</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="breakdown-list" id="breakdownList"></div>
                <span class="note-tag" id="calcNote"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Compare panel -->
        <div id="panelCompare" style="display:none;">
          <div class="calc-field" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
            <label for="cmpDegree">学位层次</label>
            <select id="cmpDegree" onchange="compare()">
              <option value="bachelor">本科 (3年均值)</option>
              <option value="master" selected>硕士 (1.5年均值)</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div id="compareTable" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;"></div>
          <span class="note-tag">数据为各国主要城市区间均值，汇率按 1 USD ≈ 7.25 CNY 换算，仅供参考</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Budget panel -->
        <div id="panelBudget" style="display:none;">
          <div class="calc-grid">
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label for="budgetCNY">可用总预算 (万人民币)</label>
              <input type="number" id="budgetCNY" placeholder="如：80" min="10" max="500" step="5" oninput="budgetCalc()">
            </div>
            <div class="calc-field">
              <label for="budgetDegree">目标学位</label>
              <select id="budgetDegree" onchange="budgetCalc()">
                <option value="master" selected>硕士</option>
                <option value="bachelor">本科</option>
                <option value="language">语言学校</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="budgetResult" style="margin-top:8px;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── COUNTRIES ── -->
<section class="section" id="countries">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">各国留学费用参考</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">7 大热门留学目的地费用概览</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">学费 + 生活费年均参考区间，点击卡片自动填入计算器</p>
    </div>
    <div class="country-grid">
      <div class="country-card reveal reveal-delay-1" onclick="prefill('AU')" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="选择澳大利亚">
        <div class="country-flag">🇦🇺</div>
        <div class="country-name">澳大利亚</div>
        <div class="country-range">年均 <strong>¥22–38 万</strong></div>
        <div class="country-tag">热门首选</div>
      </div>
      <div class="country-card reveal reveal-delay-2" onclick="prefill('UK')" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="选择英国">
        <div class="country-flag">🇬🇧</div>
        <div class="country-name">英国</div>
        <div class="country-range">年均 <strong>¥25–45 万</strong></div>
        <div class="country-tag">G5 名校</div>
      </div>
      <div class="country-card reveal reveal-delay-3" onclick="prefill('US')" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="选择美国">
        <div class="country-flag">🇺🇸</div>
        <div class="country-name">美国</div>
        <div class="country-range">年均 <strong>¥30–55 万</strong></div>
        <div class="country-tag">综合最贵</div>
      </div>
      <div class="country-card reveal reveal-delay-1" onclick="prefill('CA')" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="选择加拿大">
        <div class="country-flag">🇨🇦</div>
        <div class="country-name">加拿大</div>
        <div class="country-range">年均 <strong>¥20–36 万</strong></div>
        <div class="country-tag">移民友好</div>
      </div>
      <div class="country-card reveal reveal-delay-2" onclick="prefill('NZ')" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="选择新西兰">
        <div class="country-flag">🇳🇿</div>
        <div class="country-name">新西兰</div>
        <div class="country-range">年均 <strong>¥18–30 万</strong></div>
        <div class="country-tag">性价比高</div>
      </div>
      <div class="country-card reveal reveal-delay-3" onclick="prefill('SG')" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="选择新加坡">
        <div class="country-flag">🇸🇬</div>
        <div class="country-name">新加坡</div>
        <div class="country-range">年均 <strong>¥22–40 万</strong></div>
        <div class="country-tag">亚洲首选</div>
      </div>
      <div class="country-card reveal reveal-delay-4" onclick="prefill('HK')" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="选择香港">
        <div class="country-flag">🇭🇰</div>
        <div class="country-name">香港</div>
        <div class="country-range">年均 <strong>¥20–35 万</strong></div>
        <div class="country-tag">近便捷</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── TIPS ── -->
<section class="section tips-section" id="tips">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">省钱攻略</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">留学家庭必看：6 大实用省钱策略</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">经验丰富的留学顾问整理，帮你在不降低体验前提下最大化节省开支</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tips-grid">
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏠</div>
        <div class="tip-title">校内宿舍 vs 校外租房</div>
        <div class="tip-desc">大一优先申请校内宿舍（有补贴、省通勤）；研究生可 2–3 人合租，在主要城市年省 ¥3–8 万，选房时优先考虑步行或公交距离。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">📚</div>
        <div class="tip-title">奖学金 + 助学金组合拳</div>
        <div class="tip-desc">政府奖（如澳洲 ADB、英国 Chevening）、院校奖（Early Bird/Merit Scholarship）、私人基金会三类并行申请，实际覆盖率高达 30%–60% 学费。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">✈️</div>
        <div class="tip-title">机票抢购时机</div>
        <div class="tip-desc">开学前 3–4 个月购票最划算；中转亚洲枢纽（曼谷 / 迪拜）比直飞一般便宜 ¥1,500–4,000；用积分兑换可免机票费用。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">🍱</div>
        <div class="tip-title">餐饮 & 日常生活</div>
        <div class="tip-desc">每周采购一次食材自炊，对比外卖可节省约 60% 饮食开支。善用学生折扣（Apple / Adobe / 公共交通），年省 ¥5,000–15,000。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</div>
        <div class="tip-title">保险别超买也别漏保</div>
        <div class="tip-desc">澳洲 OSHC、英国 IHS 是强制险，美国各校自购计划差异大；额外旅行险 + 电子设备险常被忽视，合理组合比套餐省 ¥1,000–3,000/年。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="tip-icon" aria-hidden="true">💱</div>
        <div class="tip-title">换汇 & 转账策略</div>
        <div class="tip-desc">避开银行柜台高手续费；Wise / 招行跨境汇款相差可达 1.5%–3%；若家庭每年汇款 ¥20 万，手续费差额高达 ¥3,000–6,000。</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── SCHOLARSHIP ── -->
<section class="section scholarship-section" id="scholarship">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">主要奖学金</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">热门留学奖学金一览</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">覆盖 5 个热门目的国，每年都有新一轮申请机会</p>
    </div>
    <div class="scholar-grid">
      <div class="scholar-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="scholar-flag">🇦🇺</div>
        <div class="scholar-name">澳大利亚政府奖学金 (Australia Awards)</div>
        <div class="scholar-amount">最高覆盖全额学费 + 生活费</div>
        <div class="scholar-desc">针对发展中国家学生，涵盖学费、生活费、往返机票及健康保险，每年开放申请窗口。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scholar-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="scholar-flag">🇬🇧</div>
        <div class="scholar-name">英国 Chevening 奖学金</div>
        <div class="scholar-amount">学费 + 生活费 + 机票全覆盖</div>
        <div class="scholar-desc">英国外交部颁发，面向全球有领导力潜质的优秀学生，每年约 1,700 个名额，竞争激烈。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scholar-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="scholar-flag">🇨🇦</div>
        <div class="scholar-name">加拿大各省政府奖学金</div>
        <div class="scholar-amount">年均 CAD 5,000–20,000</div>
        <div class="scholar-desc">安大略省、BC 省等均设有省级国际生奖学金，叠加院校奖励可大幅降低留学成本。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scholar-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="scholar-flag">🇸🇬</div>
        <div class="scholar-name">新加坡政府奖学金 (SINGA)</div>
        <div class="scholar-amount">全额博士奖学金</div>
        <div class="scholar-desc">针对理工科博士生，由新加坡科研局资助，包含学费、生活津贴及安家费，竞争度高但含金量十足。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scholar-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="scholar-flag">🎓</div>
        <div class="scholar-name">各院校 Early Bird 奖学金</div>
        <div class="scholar-amount">学费减免 10%–25%</div>
        <div class="scholar-desc">澳、英、加、新等主要院校均设置早鸟优惠，提前 6–12 个月确认录取可直接减免学费，申请成本极低。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scholar-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="scholar-flag">🏆</div>
        <div class="scholar-name">院校 Merit Scholarship</div>
        <div class="scholar-amount">高 GPA 可获 20%–50% 减免</div>
        <div class="scholar-desc">以 GPA / 学术成就为标准，部分 G8 / QS Top 100 院校无需单独申请，录取时自动评定。</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── FAQ ── -->
<section class="section" id="faq">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">常见问题</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">留学费用规划高频问题</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>计算器的数据来源是什么，能有多准确？</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">本计算器数据来源于各国政府官网、院校公开招生信息及留学服务机构公开的费用区间报告，每季度人工核对更新。由于学费因专业、院校、学生背景各异，生活费受个人生活方式影响，<strong>所有结果仅供规划参考</strong>，实际费用以院校录取通知书及官方生活费指导为准，建议与专业顾问确认。</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>留学费用里通常包含哪些项目？机票每年都要算吗？</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">主要分五类：<strong>① 学费</strong>（最大头，专业差异巨大，医学/法律通常是均价 2–3 倍）<strong>② 住宿费</strong>（校内宿舍 vs 校外租房差距约 20%–50%）<strong>③ 日常生活费</strong>（餐饮/交通/通讯/日用品）<strong>④ 海外医疗保险</strong>（澳洲 OSHC、英国 IHS 是强制项目）<strong>⑤ 往返机票</strong>（本计算器按首年单次计入，短期回国按需另算）。签证费、申请费、课本费、户外活动等属于小项，本计算器未单独列出，建议额外预留 ¥5,000–15,000/年。</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>澳洲和英国同是硕士，为什么费用差距这么大？</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">主要有三个驱动因素：<strong>① 学制长短</strong>：英国硕士通常 1 年制，澳洲 1.5–2 年，相同年度费率时总额差异明显。<strong>② 城市生活成本</strong>：伦敦住宿+生活费远高于曼彻斯特或墨尔本，同一国家内不同城市差距可达 40%。<strong>③ 汇率波动</strong>：澳元/英镑兑人民币汇率年度波动约 5%–15%，会显著影响实际到手金额，建议锁定汇率或分批购汇。</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>新加坡和香港生活费很高，有没有办法降低？</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">两地生活成本高，但有几个可行策略：<strong>新加坡</strong>——NUS/NTU 宿舍名额有限但价格低于市场 30%–50%，尽早申请；食堂（Canteen/Hawker Center）用餐 SGD 3–6 远低于餐馆，坚持自食是最大省钱点。<strong>香港</strong>——HKUST、HKU 等宿舍竞争激烈，可考虑沙田、大埔等新界地区，通勤 30–45 分钟但租金省 HKD 2,000–4,000/月；港府公共交通学生优惠覆盖 MTR + 公交，年省约 HKD 6,000。</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>如何评估自己需要携带多少启动资金？</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
